column2: SSH agent authentication for git4idea, svn4idea

column3:
Hi Charles,
Have you submitted a contributor agreement? If not, could you please download the PDF from http://www.jetbrains.org/display/IJOS/Contributor+Agreement and print it out, scan and send to contribute@jetbrains.com? Thanks!
This is a work-for-hire for my employer; I've asked our legal department to approve a CA, and will report back after it's executed.
Any chance code review could happen in the interim, so we're ready to merge when the paperwork is ready?
Closing this pull request -- updated version to be submitted from corporate github account (having a contributor agreement executed on behalf of my employer, which owns copyright to this code).
